## Switch to Workspace 2 (Edit)
## Alt + 2
bindsym Mod1+2 exec swayworkspace navigate 2


## Switch to Workspace 3 (Web)
## Alt + 3
bindsym Mod1+3 exec swayworkspace navigate 3


